      <title>瑞典电力运营商 SBB 被标普评为选择性违约</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/swedish-landlord-sbb-cut-to-selective-default-by-s-p</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔全球评级将 Norden AB 的长期发行人信用评级从之前的 CCC 下调至选择性违约，同时将其所有接受交换要约的评级高级无担保债务的发行人评级下调至 D。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/swedish-landlord-sbb-cut-to-selective-default-by-s-p</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
