      <title>台湾反对派首次动用新权力 调查政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/taiwan-s-opposition-probes-government-in-first-use-of-new-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾反对派立法者首次利用一项有争议的新法律来对抗执政党民进党政府，加剧了激烈的政治斗争，并可能妨碍赖清德总统上任仅几周后的议程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/taiwan-s-opposition-probes-government-in-first-use-of-new-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:53:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本 2024 年薪酬协议达成，涨幅达 5.1%，创 33 年来最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/japan-2024-pay-deals-conclude-with-5-1-gain-most-in-33-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据日本最大工会组织的最终统计结果，日本年度工资谈判以 30 多年来的最高涨幅结束，证实了央行寻求的工资上涨趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/japan-2024-pay-deals-conclude-with-5-1-gain-most-in-33-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:50:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰合作银行的 Foley 表示，法国僵局不应给市场带来安慰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-gridlock-shouldn-t-comfort-markets-rabobank-s-foley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰合作银行货币策略师简·福利 (Jane Foley) 表示，周日法国大选后出现悬浮议会的前景不应该让投资者感到高兴，因为这将意味着预算陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-gridlock-shouldn-t-comfort-markets-rabobank-s-foley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:49:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
